div.p: Generated predictions by the DDDBN model for spring zooplankton (A), fall zooplankton (B), white shrimp (C), brown shrimp (D), red snapper (E) and King mackerel (F). The series marked with stars denote the predictions as opposed to the observed standardized data denoted by circles. 95% confidence intervals (highlighted in gray color) report bootstrap predictionsâ€™ mean and standard deviation. Note the negative scale is due to standardization.
